projects.title: Dreamer Ecommerce Store
projects.shortDesc: Ecommerce store with add to Cart functionality
projects.desc: A Django-based e-commerce website with admin is a web application built using the Python Django framework, specifically designed to facilitate online shopping. The admin interface is a powerful tool within this setup, allowing administrators to manage various aspects of the website efficiently. Product Management: Admins can add, edit, and remove products, including details like name, description, price, images, and categories. Product Variations: Handle product variations (e.g., size, color) to offer diverse options.Inventory Tracking: Maintain accurate stock levels to avoid out-of-stock situations.
